24/12/2002
PODGORICA, Montenegro, Yugoslavia -- Zoran Sami, chairman of Monday's (23 December) session of the constitutional subcommission, said the panel is expected to reach full agreement Tuesday on issues related to the law on enforcing the charter.
During Monday's session, the sides discussed the role and structure of the central bank in the new federation.
The parties are reportedly close to reaching a compromise on federation representation in international institutions.
(B92, Tanjug - 23/12/02)
